### Get All categories
GET http://localhost:4022/categories HTTP/1.1

### Get Limited categories
GET http://localhost:4022/categories?page=2&limit=1 HTTP/1.1

### Get Searched categories
GET http://localhost:4022/categories/search?text=Electronics HTTP/1.1

### Create product
POST http://localhost:4022/categories/create HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "clothing"
}

### Update product
